# Presentation Layer Rules

## Widget Structure
- One widget per file
- Use StatelessWidget when possible
- Extract reusable widgets to shared components
- Keep build methods clean and readable

## UI Guidelines
- Follow Material Design guidelines
- Use theme colors and text styles from theme directory
- Support both light and dark themes
- Implement responsive layouts

## State Management
- Use BLoC/Cubit pattern for complex state
- Keep presentation logic separate from business logic
- Handle loading, success, and error states
- Show appropriate feedback to users

## Navigation
- Use named routes
- Handle deep linking properly
- Implement proper back button behavior
- Pass minimal data between screens

## Form Handling
- Validate input on change and submit
- Show clear error messages
- Handle keyboard properly
- Support form state persistence

## Accessibility
- Add semantic labels
- Support screen readers
- Maintain proper contrast ratios
- Handle different text sizes
